review: I don't know how to rate this. On the one hand, the black icons are excellent and look great. On the other hand, it doesn't have icons for every app (naturally). And the contrast between normal colored icons and these icons is just too jarring. It becomes pretty much unusable because of this. I uninstalled the icon pack after 10 minutes.

So good that it is hard to believe it is free! The aesthetics are on another level altogether and the adaptation for apps not originally part of the pack is incredibly consistent and thoughtful. Thank you for sharing your talent with the rest of us and making our screens look more beautiful than before!

It's really gd the only down side for me is there's no option to switch it to dark icons in dark mode some people just like there phone fully black so it would be nice if u could add that as a option.

This is a very good app, the icons are well designed but there's just one thing i want , and that is being able to change the blackness, i don't like a very dark black and i want something i little tint of gray, anyways ill give 4 stars

Don't get me wrong, the icons here are great. But the problem is when I change the default app icon given by this app, after a while it will change to something completely different and unrelated. This happens randomly and yeah, it's an annoying bug. But other than that, the included wallpapers is a nice touch, there are little no ads inside the app, and it's easy to use. I am willing to change my review as soon as they fix it :)

I use it along with microsoft launcher and i can't live without it. Yes, it may be a bit difficult to see at times, especially with dark wallpapers (i have bing daily as my wallpaper, so it changes every day), but overall it's way better than the standard look. It turnes my mobile desktop from a chaotic mess into a neat and consistent masterpiece. An idea for another icon pack is to be like this but have white borders, so that they are consantly visible, and neat.

It's a huge collection, and as others said, it'll benefit from an alphabetical index. But once everything is set up, the phone looks simply great. As for the request, it might be useful to put a line in the Help mentioning that you have to choose email once the bundle is ready, it confused me for a while.
Could u plz add xos launcher plz I have xos launcher so I couldn't use this icons. So plz add xos launcher. Love the icons and some icons r missing.

Huge pack with consistent updates and great silhouettes.

Very clean and comprehensive. Could use some generic icons for the oddball apps that no one else uses (even just letters and numbers). Could be better organized - scrolling through 7000 icons to pick one that starts with y, for example, is annoying.

I don't usually review apps, but this one is spectacular. It's free and supports so many apps. All other packs I've tried I had to edit unsupported icons individually, but when I applied this one it. just. worked. Every single app on my phone, even YouTube Vanced. Best icon pack I've ever tried

Nice work on the minimalistic design while still keeping depth. The large number of icons is great too. Really well done! The only reason my rating isn't higher is due to recent crashes. but other than that, I'm pleased. Ta.

Saw some YouTuber using this icon pack/app and decided to download it. Very happy with it and it's made my phone look completely different and amazing. Includes icons for most apps although a few are missing. But the developer keeps updating it I guess, so that's good. Great job.
Had to download launchers which did not work and almost couldn't disable one of them. Anxiety fuel.

While searching i had to make sure i selected all icons otherwise it would not search and crash instead and in many case it crashes even if you select all icons.

Great pack. Naturally it doesn't have everything I use but it has A LOT. I wish Google would allow overlays just to Black out the original icons for symmetry but it's all gravy; I just use the pack with Sesame so every once in a while I see an unsupported icon.

wonderful app, there is many icons what i like
